<br />\n你以為一間公司係SIMCITY<br />\n話搬去第二度就即時可以無影響照常營業?<br />\n遷冊唔等於改營業地點<br />\n<br />\n前海、上海成日話取代香港<br />\n搞左20年都取代唔到半滴啦<br />\n<br />\n你試下搬間公司去上海, 睇下係咪同係香港營業一樣, 搵到同樣既客?<br />\n<br />\n你夠唔夠16歲?"},{"pid":"0860b53cbf396512ed34aabcea918e0ee1312158","tid":434733,"uid":44777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:05:51.000Z","msg":"加泰獨立 其實係對歐盟有利啵<br />\n只要歐盟肯認佢地 佢地都樂意同歐盟合作<br />\n咁重要既經濟體 大把錢 貿易 <br />\n我諗唔到點破壞歐盟"},{"pid":"591e0f720df72678a2ecef0bfe284f53b1de392b","tid":434733,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f89e06b72d56a958c1c7063df1cc5df3484a1084","tid":434733,"uid":683,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:09:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/231443_e1636d1ff849db66831dbba501bf2729.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F231443_e1636d1ff849db66831dbba501bf2729.jpg&h=e0249d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪即係燒到自己後欄就乜野人權民主自由都可以放埋一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n世上所有大一統機構都係雙重標準</blockquote><br />\non9<br />\n呢堆係普羅百姓唔係政治精英<br />\n<br />\n而家個個出黎反加獨既都係政治精英黎 當年邊個西方政治精英試過走出黎支持藏獨？<br />\n<br />\n將所有西人label哂做外國勢力，然後人地意見分歧個陣就出黎屌「外國勢力雙重標準」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd631917323f4448a11bd466ebcb0d67c7604b0","tid":434733,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:10:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f164bae81caaa28674abb50acc69ffa26703b57c","tid":434733,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25a42acee7697604e3a9429dba645176e346e11","tid":434733,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:10:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1900706b9b7c5638ae6548acaf2db1feac81cae8","tid":434733,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:11:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐盟執委會主席容克（Jean-Claude Juncker）13日表示，他不希望加泰隆尼亞獨立，因為這樣會鼓勵其他地區也這樣做，讓歐盟無法控制。<br />\n<br />\n容克在盧森堡大學的一場演講中說道：「如果我們允許加泰羅尼亞分離，且這並非我們的事務，其他人也會這樣做。我不想那樣。我不希望15年內歐盟由98個左右的國家組成。28個已相當困難，27個也沒比較容易，但是98個的話就不可能了。」歐盟統計局列出歐盟共有98個主要地區。<br />\n<br />\n容克並表示對歐洲的分離主義傾向「非常擔心」，並鼓勵西班牙總理拉霍伊確保局勢不會失控。<br />\n<br />\n當提到加泰隆尼亞呼籲歐盟介入調解一事時，他則表示若僅一方要求這樣做，執委會就不能調解。「若執委會或歐洲理事會主席圖斯克只因一方要求調解而涉入，這將使歐盟被大大抵制。」<br />\n<br />\n歐盟此前已表示對拉霍伊有信心，並將加泰隆尼亞視為西國內部問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2756012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F2756012&d=BkPQdImdiDAFhis9VhRU1QdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=810e6ac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2756012</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/224943_9c17df6fbe45607c8a5e70b894e6bee6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F224943_9c17df6fbe45607c8a5e70b894e6bee6.jpg&h=3ea2e4d5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">#1 光之練金術師 1 小時前</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"1cc8031de48340b39ee4bfe96873fd031815acf3","tid":434733,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8de8b5f33d006e56c0de364e53cf8e14d111a9fd","tid":434733,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實愈多獨先<span style=\"color: red;\">愈有機會組織歐盟</span><br />\n小國力弱必須互相依靠</blockquote><br />\n你叻過歐盟主席</blockquote><br />\n我地都叻唔過中國主席 所以<span style=\"color: green;\">爭取民主是不對的</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比喻不正確<br />\n摩西巴打講緊嘅唔係<span style=\"color: green;\">對錯問題</span>，而係<span style=\"color: red;\">歐盟嘅利益問題</span><br />\n講到<span style=\"color: red;\">歐盟嘅利益問題</span>歐盟主席比任何人更清楚</blockquote><br />\n竟然冇人代答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國主席就中國嘅利益問題最清楚<br />\n識得分中國同中共未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa011b1c6056f2d766aa2aafd9fae25b9e143a94","tid":434733,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實愈多獨先愈有機會組織歐盟<br />\n小國力弱必須互相依靠</blockquote><br />\ntrue. 但歐盟實際上係德法俱樂部，德法唔會比歐元區既中型國家冧檔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下加泰點回應囉<br />\n<br />\n歐盟比承認獨立, 入返歐盟, 我科多D水比歐盟, 頂多D西班牙債都OK<br />\n(國民辛苦一排, 加泰有經濟實力)<br />\n<br />\n歐盟同西班牙反對, 我一樣獨立, 但你孤立我, 我就一蚊都唔比, 同支那及英國發展多D貿易<br />\n<br />\nGAME THEORY黎講, 歐盟應該要受佢玩</blockquote><br />\n你計漏左<br />\n會有好多歐盟公司離開加泰<br />\n你有咩本錢同支那英國做貿易<br />\n公司返去西班牙開張<br />\n搶埋你客仔<br />\n加泰自己好快收晒皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n獨立應該會窮過以前</blockquote><br />\n你以為一間公司係SIMCITY<br />\n話搬去第二度就即時可以無影響照常營業?<br />\n遷冊唔等於改營業地點<br />\n<br />\n前海、上海成日話取代香港<br />\n搞左20年都取代唔到半滴啦<br />\n<br />\n你試下搬間公司去上海, 睇下係咪同係香港營業一樣, 搵到同樣既客?<br />\n<br />\n你夠唔夠16歲?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鹽田吞吐量已經過左香港<br />\n深圳做高科技已屈晒香港<br />\n上海做經濟都已經差唔多追到<br />\n半滴都可能更岩形容呢20年香港發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原地踏步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要不是97<br />\n哪有這麼多公司離開香港<br />\nHSBC<br />\n中共對香港破壞太大"},{"pid":"716192af253e1ca7fa8e1bd6752da43e198d555c","tid":434733,"uid":68728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"由歐債 Greece 破產 到難民 再到而家加泰獨立<br />\n<br />\n已經可以見到EU會步入歷史舞台"},{"pid":"0e48224aeba89fad712823bc0935e44d68811640","tid":434733,"uid":81518,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:19:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a239028207c011918bcac147828ad8d798922d91","tid":434733,"uid":48670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"成個歐盟都五毛黎<br />\n等歐爆啦 屌"},{"pid":"9616a22627d04811f22065feb100980dd81da879","tid":434733,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實愈多獨先<span style=\"color: red;\">愈有機會組織歐盟</span><br />\n小國力弱必須互相依靠</blockquote><br />\n你叻過歐盟主席</blockquote><br />\n我地都叻唔過中國主席 所以<span style=\"color: green;\">爭取民主是不對的</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比喻不正確<br />\n摩西巴打講緊嘅唔係<span style=\"color: green;\">對錯問題</span>，而係<span style=\"color: red;\">歐盟嘅利益問題</span><br />\n講到<span style=\"color: red;\">歐盟嘅利益問題</span>歐盟主席比任何人更清楚</blockquote><br />\n竟然冇人代答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國主席就中國嘅利益問題最清楚<br />\n識得分中國同中共未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>加泰獨立 其實係對歐盟有利啵<br />\n只要歐盟肯認佢地 佢地都樂意同歐盟合作<br />\n咁重要既經濟體 大把錢 貿易 <br />\n我諗唔到點破壞歐盟</blockquote><br />\n得啦，不如你都去應徵歐盟主席顧問好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎張非紅褲子足球評述員名單俾你去問佢地幾時考青年軍好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":