r />\n另外一提 蘇格蘭都想獨立啦<br />\n但人地重想加入eu 唔通咁樣又分裂eu</blockquote><br />\n其實個情況好複雜嘅.<br />\n<br />\n非常簡單咁講, 歐盟係唔想地區可以晌冇主權國政府同意下獨立到, 因為咁樣大把地區有樣學樣.<br />\n<br />\n至於蘇格蘭就係特別例子, 因為佢地嘅獨立運動係獲主權國認同, 搞得成機會大好多, 歐盟自然唔會出口得罪個可能成為成員國嘅國家."},{"pid":"471e03a397d74a784eecfa68c9545b0516b9541f","tid":434733,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T21:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5706735340a30dccde00e8edb63cb2be061e23","tid":434733,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T01:01:54.000Z","msg":"歐共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1982cf701c2086a005b21340cc26360ac5366513","tid":434733,"uid":46749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T01:09:12.000Z","msg":"佢只係直接證明: 歐盟就係靠錢維繫既團體, 其他層面上既融合係完全失敗"},{"pid":"94a21c8b945f9f247ad648e1c9d14b30db402c04","tid":434733,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T01:19:41.000Z","msg":"唸起以前法國同反法同盟既歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a3c008e6888dfb6f4f6dd4fd4ad4f08ae633ac","tid":434733,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T02:21:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實愈多獨先<span style=\"color: red;\">愈有機會組織歐盟</span><br />\n小國力弱必須互相依靠</blockquote><br />\n你叻過歐盟主席</blockquote><br />\n我地都叻唔過中國主席 所以<span style=\"color: green;\">爭取民主是不對的</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比喻不正確<br />\n摩西巴打講緊嘅唔係<span style=\"color: green;\">對錯問題</span>，而係<span style=\"color: red;\">歐盟嘅利益問題</span><br />\n講到<span style=\"color: red;\">歐盟嘅利益問題</span>歐盟主席比任何人更清楚</blockquote><br />\n竟然冇人代答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/